73", "uri": "https://scontent-sea1-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982452_1819228065253606_407037206585227872_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=VPw7TP_MSUIQ7kNvgFkHUCK&_nc_ht=scontent-sea1-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCFUaL3txn5ZLocCVYlE-mJbyha_Gamli89Qbqlm2UmSw&oe=6710E60A"}, "display_name": "Pinfall", "keywords": [], "long_description": "Pinfall: The Ultimate VR Bowling Experience\n\nWelcome to \"Pinfall,\" where the classic sport of bowling transcends the ordinary and enters the realm of immersive virtual reality. Prepare to embark on a cosmic adventure that transforms traditional bowling into an exhilarating and futuristic experience. Whether you're a seasoned bowler or new to the game, \"Pinfall\" offers a fresh and captivating way to enjoy this beloved sport.\nGame Overview\n\n\"Pinfall\" is a cutting-edge VR game that redefines the bowling experience by placing players in a vibrant cosmic arena. The game challenges your precision, skill, and timing as you aim to score points by knocking down pins in various celestial-themed lanes. Each game session offers a unique adventure, filled with stunning visuals and dynamic gameplay.", "short_description": "Pinfall: The Ultimate VR Bowling Experience\n\nWelcome to \"Pinfall,\" where the classic sport of bowling transcends the ordinary and enters the realm of immersive virtual reality. Prepare to embark on a cosmic adventure that transforms traditional bowling into an exhilarating and futuristic experience. Whether you're a seasoned bowler or new to the game, \"Pinfall\" offers a fresh and captivating way to enjoy this beloved sport."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://sites.google.com/view/pinfall/privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "TT Invention", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://sites.google.com/view/pinfall", "category": null, "comfort_rating": null, "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534